HEADWORD: Shredding
<hw>Shred"ding</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of cutting or tearing into shreds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is cut or torn off; a piece.</def>
